1
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,640
Aling.

2
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,480
You want to save her.

3
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,320
You can save her.

4
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:26,300
Her life force has scattered.

5
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,820
If you want to save her,

6
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,840
you must trade your life for hers.

7
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,520
I am willing.

8
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,240
A thought arises.

9
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:40,440
Incense burns.

10
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,880
Three souls gather.

11
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,460
With your flesh and blood,

12
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:48,000
exchange for her rebirth.

13
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:51,160
Return, soul.

14
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,640
This is Lingxi Incense,

15
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,480
made from your life.

16
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,760
Only after lighting it can she be reborn.

17
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:05,450
But whether you can change fate

18
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:07,880
depends on the two of you.

19
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,720
Where am I?

20
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:15,040
What is this incense for?

21
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,370
Why is the incense shorter?

22
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,530
Is it related to my rebirth?

23
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,610
Sure enough,

24
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,810
I'm back here again.

25
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:44,040
Why is only half of the incense left?

26
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:51,970
Who's there?

27
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,400
Your Highness,

28
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,040
you've been feeling down lately

29
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:03,960
and haven't been eating well.

30
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,890
I made some soup.

31
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,080
Please have some.

32
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:09,920
Since this incense is burning away Yunxi's life,

33
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:10,920
if I put it out,

34
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,640
will it save him?

35
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:14,960
Even if

36
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:18,050
I have to give my own life in return.

37
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,340
Your Highness,

38
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,090
why did you put out the incense?

39
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,800
You can see this incense?

40
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,520
Yes.

41
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,800
What is going on?

42
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,980
Only I could see this incense before.

43
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:43,760
Your Majesty.

44
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:46,740
His Majesty invites you to Changan Hall.

45
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,040
At this hour,

46
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,080
isn't he reviewing memorials?

47
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,040
Why call me over?

48
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:57,760
A-Ling.

49
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,240
This memorial concerns the people's livelihood.

50
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,880
It must be reviewed carefully.

51
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,480
Look here.

52
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:13,520
Su Kuang.

53
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,820
The Empress looks unwell.

54
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,280
Summon the Imperial Physician.

55
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:18,760
Yes.

56
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:20,410
Don't go.

57
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,640
I'm fine.

58
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,760
I feel fine.

59
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:27,280
It must be the backlash from extinguishing the incense.

60
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:28,320
I wonder how many more months

61
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,280
I can hold on for.

62
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,080
Do not hide your illness.

63
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:32,960
Time is precious.

64
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,800
Let's look at the memorials.

65
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,320
Look.

66
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,170
Look at this one.

67
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,159
Poor me, with one foot in the grave.

68
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,400
Just to keep Li Yunxi from finding out,

69
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,880
I have to put on an act here,

70
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,480
learning to review memorials.

71
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,080
Look here.

72
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,040
Stop teaching me.

73
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,600
I have no talent for this.

74
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:59,400
Take care of your health and live a few more years.

75
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,640
I need to go out and pick a fight.

76
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,120
Or I'll suffocate to death.

77
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:02,650
Go fight.

78
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,840
You're awake.

79
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,570
What happened to me?

80
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,280
You're pregnant.

81
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:20,760
I felt it too.

82
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,040
I'm pregnant.

83
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,650
What did you say?

84
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:29,680
You are two months pregnant.

85
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,960
Hanxing said you haven't been eating or sleeping well.

86
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,280
You were feeling so unwell.

87
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,540
Why didn't you tell me?

88
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,720
I didn't know either.

89
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,320
In all these lives,

90
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:43,460
this is my first time being pregnant.

91
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:45,409
You're going to be a mother.

92
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:47,300
Don't be reckless from now on.

93
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,960
No more fighting.

94
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,400
And no wielding weapons.

95
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:51,330
I won't. I got it.

96
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:58,440
Take your medicine first.

97
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,770
I'll check on you later.

98
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:07,820
Your Highness,

99
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,600
why do you look so unhappy?

100
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,040
I do not know

101
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,290
if I can live to see this child born.

102
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,530
It is just a pity that this child

103
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,660
came at the wrong time.

104
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:19,960
God forbid!

105
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,840
You must not say such things.

106
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:27,280
I hope I can give birth to this child safely.

107
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:32,600
Your Highness is in good health.

108
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,440
I am fine.

109
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,240
Yes, Your Highness.

110
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,600
You checked His Majesty's pulse recently.

111
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,600
How is his health?

112
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,320
His Majesty looks a bit better.

113
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:47,409
Is it because I extinguished the incense,

114
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:50,280
so the backlash has stopped?

115
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,420
You seem to be in a good mood today.

116
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,410
You added notes to the parts

117
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,200
I didn't understand.

118
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:23,120
Doesn't that make it easier

119
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,200
for you to read?

120
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:30,880
Your Majesty looks well today too.

121
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:39,960
Don't look at me.

122
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,059
Look at the memorials.

123
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:42,880
Okay.

124
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,720
Teach me how to read them.

125
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,080
Okay.

126
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:51,760
Look here.

127
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,260
These concern the people's livelihood.

128
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,960
These are about the economy.

129
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,240
And these points,

130
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,480
must be prioritized.

131
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,040
Especially those regarding people's livelihood,

132
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,700
you must pay close attention.

133
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,640
If you are tired,

134
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,490
lean on me and sleep for a while.

135
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,520
Your Highness, you're awake.

136
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,280
The little prince just fell asleep after feeding.

137
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:56,080
It's been a month since the birth,

138
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,680
and you've recovered well.

139
00:09:57,960 --> 00:10:00,280
Imperial Physician Wang says you are healthy.

140
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:03,010
You're almost back to your pre-pregnancy state.

141
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,960
Where is His Majesty?

142
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,170
I haven't seen him for days.

143
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,800
Why hasn't he come to see me and the baby?

144
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:17,760
His Majesty...

145
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,960
The Imperial Physician said a few days ago...

146
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:20,600
that he feared...

147
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,260
His Majesty wouldn't make it.

148
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:30,560
Last winter,

149
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:33,160
His Majesty suddenly took something

150
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,600
from the window sill of Jile Hall.

151
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:37,480
And he asked me to light a short incense stick on the sill.

152
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,040
You extinguished the incense,

153
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:41,300
so His Majesty said not to light it again.

154
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:43,160
Because Your Highness is pregnant,

155
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:45,200
His Majesty forbade us from telling you.

156
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,160
But now,

157
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,580
His Majesty...

158
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,040
Li Yunxi.

159
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,360
So you didn't lose your memory in this life.

160
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:01,290
You anticipated everything I did.

161
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:05,200
You kept me completely in the dark.

162
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:09,720
Yunxi.

163
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:12,560
Yunxi.

164
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:15,400
Yunxi.

165
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,360
Yunxi.

166
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:31,840
Yunxi.

167
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:32,640
Don't cry.

168
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:36,200
It seems I...

169
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:39,400
can't go to Jiangnan with you.

170
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,840
You must live well.

171
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:50,250
The Lingxi Incense has burned out.

172
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,840
I leave the rest...

173
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,360
to you.

174
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,080
I, Li Yunxi, swear here,

175
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:02,640
in this life and the next,

176
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,600
you will be my only woman.

177
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,880
I will always be by your side.

178
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:10,560
But marrying you,

179
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,240
I don't regret it.

180
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:14,340
Even if we torment each other,

181
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,320
we shall do so for a lifetime.

182
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,440
I'm sorry, Aling.

183
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:21,840
I can no longer be with you and our child.

184
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,460
Your Highness,

185
00:12:39,920 --> 00:12:41,560
in the hidden compartment ahead,

186
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:43,690
is something His Majesty left for you.

187
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:56,680
So, the real Lingxi Incense is here.

188
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:09,840
One incense, one life, one cycle of rebirth.

189
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:15,080
One thought, one trial, one lotus blooms.

190
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,920
Burn this life to fuel the spirit flame,

191
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:25,040
leaving only obsession

192
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,720
lingering around the altar.

193
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:31,680
Aling.

194
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:36,920
If there is an afterlife,

195
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,400
let us meet again.
